=== 开发 ===
影片剧本题为《与敌同行》（{{lang|en|''Running with the bulls''}}）<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.indianexpress.com/news/darpok-kalki-misses-the-znmd-fun/810488/|title='Darpok' Kalki misses the ZNMD fun|work=The Indian Express|accessdate=2011-11-28|date=2011-07-29|author=IE Agencies}}</ref>，经过三个月的创作于2009年11月完成<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Bollywood/Katrina-wasn-t-the-first-choice-for-Zindagi-Na/Article1-718358.aspx |title=Katrina wasn't the first choice for Zindagi Na... |work=Hindustan Times |accessdate=2011-11-28 |date=2011-08-08 |author=Serena Menon |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110810083523/http://www.hindustantimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/Katrina-wasn-t-the-first-choice-for-Zindagi-Na/Article1-718358.aspx |archivedate=2011-08-10 }}</ref>。卓娅和{{le|瑞玛·卡吉蒂|Reema Kagti|卡吉蒂}}结合现实生活的观察，以她的弟弟法尔汗·阿赫塔尔（{{lang|en|Farhan Akhtar}}）为原型创作了伊姆兰一角。阿赫塔尔写了电影的台词<ref>{{cite web|url=http://newindianexpress.com/entertainment/interviews/article418533.ece|title=Zoya Akhtar on ‘Zindagi Na Milegi Dobara’|work=The New Indian Express|accessdate=2011-11-28|date=2011-07-13|author=Neelima Menon|archive-date=2014-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221170127/http://www.newindianexpress.com/entertainment/interviews/article418533.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他表示，影片的主题“关于三位处在人生中许诺边缘的家伙”<ref name="BHFI">{{cite web|url=http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/moviemicro/features/type/view/id/1865|title="Don 2 follows SRK's character into a different adventure" – Farhan|publisher=Bollywood Hungama|accessdate=2012-02-20|date=2011-02-19|author=Subhash K. Jha|archive-date=2014-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140203054748/http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/moviemicro/features/type/view/id/1865|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他们使用{{le|贾韦德·阿赫塔尔|Javed Akhtar}}的诗句作为[[画外音|画外音]]，因为他们觉得诗句增加了角色的深度，赋予他们的情感声音<ref name=zoyahindu/>。卡特丽娜加盟项目剧组后，一首特别的诗为卡特丽娜的角色专门写就<ref name="BHP"/>。墨西哥是首选的取景地，但后来由于高潮部分出现了奔牛场面且卓拉想要一个有着多元历史、文化和体育国家而改往西班牙<ref name=zoyahindu>{{cite news|title=Love, life and friends|url=http://www.thehindu.com/life-and-style/metroplus/article2238243.ece?homepage=true|work=The Hindu|accessdate=2011-07-18|date=2011-07-18|author=Sangeetha Devi Dundoo|archive-date=2011-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110720133719/http://www.thehindu.com/life-and-style/metroplus/article2238243.ece?homepage=true|dead-url=no}}</ref>。影片上映档期由于最初选定的剪辑师影片查丹·阿罗拉（{{lang|en|Chandan Arora}}）生病，他们必须重新进行剪辑而三度改期<ref name="Editing"/>。

=== 选角 ===
最初，[[伊姆兰·汗|伊姆兰·汗]]和[[兰比尔·卡普尔|兰比尔·卡普尔]]理应扮演三位主角中的其中两位，但他们由于希望共同出演自己的作品而婉拒<ref>{{cite news|url=http://entertainment.oneindia.in/bollywood/gupshup/2009/imran-ranbir-zoya-100909.html|title=Imran Khan, Ranbir Kapoor opt out of Zoya’s film|publisher=Oneindia.in|accessdate=2010-05-14|date=2009-09-10|archive-date=2012-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121022170608/http://entertainment.oneindia.in/bollywood/gupshup/2009/imran-ranbir-zoya-100909.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。弟弟法拉汗·阿克塔尔帮助卓娅创作她的处女作《{{le|幸运机会|Luck By Chance}}》，还写了本片的台词，因此卓娅认为他能知晓她在这部电影中究竟想要些什么<ref name=zoyacastbh/>。他是第一位加盟影片的演员<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mid-day.com/entertainment/2009/oct/291009-zoya-akhtar-road-movie-farhan.htm|accessdate=2011-07-21|title=Zoya Akhtar's next a road movie, brother Farhan to play lead|publisher=Mid Day|date=2009-10-29|author=Indo-Asian News Service|archive-date=2012-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120223131827/http://www.mid-day.com/entertainment/2009/oct/291009-zoya-akhtar-road-movie-farhan.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他定义他的角色为一个“有意思的角色”、一个“很长时间以来没有认真做过事情的家伙”<ref name="BHFI"/>。赫里尼克因为是她最心仪的一个演员，而被选为另一位主角<ref name=zoyacast />。敲定两位主演后，她想要“不仅在视觉上跟两人很般配，还能给阵容带来一些新鲜事物”的演员。她请求此前在{{le|瑞玛·卡吉蒂|Reema Kagti}}的《{{le|蜜月旅行社|Honeymoon Travels Pvt. Ltd.}}》中有过合作的朋友阿布依参演角色<ref name=zoyacastbh>{{cite news|title="Zindagi Na Milegi Dobara is also the philosophy of the film" – Zoya Akhtar|url=http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/movies/features/type/view/id/2444/%22Zindagi+Na+Milegi+Dobara+is+also+the+philosophy+of+the+film%22+-+Zoya+Akhtar|publisher=Bollywood Hungama|accessdate=2011-07-18|date=2011-07-18|author=Satish Sundaresan|archive-date=2016-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160813082855/http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/movies/features/type/view/id/2444/%22Zindagi+Na+Milegi+Dobara+is+also+the+philosophy+of+the+film%22+-+Zoya+Akhtar|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

至于莱拉一角，卓娅希望找一个愿意[[水肺潜水|水肺潜水]]的“乡音”未改的半印度半白人女孩<ref name=zoyacast>{{cite news|title=Hrithik Roshan is Zoya's all-time favourite|url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/hrithik-roshan-is-zoya%C3%A2%E2%82%AC%E2%84%A2s-all--time-favourite/1/144781.html|work=India Today|accessdate=2011-12-31|date=2011-07-14|author=Priyanka Srivastava, Sonali Joshi and Lipika Varma|archive-date=2016-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818114842/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/hrithik-roshan-is-zoya%C3%A2%E2%82%AC%E2%84%A2s-all--time-favourite/1/144781.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。很多女孩在纽约和伦敦试镜。后来在一个派对上，她碰到了卡特丽娜·卡芙并选中她<ref name=rediffspainzoya/>。她的角色据称是“一位自由奔放的女孩，一位心灵游子，本质上是个放荡不羁的吉普赛人<ref name="BHP">{{cite news|url=http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/news/1231316/Javed-Akhtar-to-pen-down-special-poem-for-Katrinas-character-in-Zoyas-film|title=Javed Akhtar to pen down special poem for Katrina's character in Zoya's film|publisher=Bollywood Hungama|accessdate=2012-02-20|date=2010-06-17|author=Subhash K. Jha|archive-date=2014-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141109123143/http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/news/1231316/Javed-Akhtar-to-pen-down-special-poem-for-Katrinas-character-in-Zoyas-film|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”卓娅想与曾在《{{le|后现代激情|Dev. D}}》和《{{le|穿黄靴子的女孩|That Girl in Yellow Boots}}》上见到的卡琪合作。她认为卡琪娜塔莎一角的性格，因为她“有喜感，但不算拔尖”<ref>{{cite news |url=http://movies.ndtv.com/movie_story.aspx?section=Movies&Id=ENTEN20110179547&keyword=bollywood&subcatg=MOVIESINDIA&nid=117658 |accessdate=2011-07-21 |title=Zoya is all praises for Katrina and Kalki |work=NDTV |date=2011-07-08 |author=Indo-Asian News Service |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110711123413/http://movies.ndtv.com/movie_story.aspx?section=Movies&Id=ENTEN20110179547&keyword=bollywood&subcatg=MOVIESINDIA&nid=117658 |archivedate=2011-07-11 }}</ref>。阿里亚德娜被选为努丽雅一角，因为她喜欢她在2009年西班牙电影《埃洛伊塞》（{{lang|es|''Eloise''}}）中的表现。影片完整演出阵容于2010年4月公开<ref>{{cite news |url=http://movies.ndtv.com/movie_Story.aspx?id=ENTEN20100139646&keyword=&subcatg= |title=Zindagi Na Milegi Dobara cast and crew |work=NDTV |accessdate=2011-06-28 |date=2010-04-27 |author=Press Trust of India |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120118201237/http://movies.ndtv.com/movie_Story.aspx?id=ENTEN20100139646&keyword=&subcatg= |archivedate=2012-01-18 }}</ref>。

=== 摄制 ===
影片于2010年6月开拍，在西班牙的巴塞罗那、潘普洛纳、[[布尼奥尔|布尼奥尔]]和[[安达鲁西亚|安达鲁西亚]]、英国、埃及和孟买取景<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Bollywood/Working-with-Hrithik-and-Katrina-made-me-nervous/Article1-631573.aspx |title=‘Working with Hrithik and Katrina made me nervous’ |work=Hindustan Times |accessdate=2011-06-28 |date=2010-11-28 |author=Priyanka Jain |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110208055300/http://www.hindustantimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/Working-with-Hrithik-and-Katrina-made-me-nervous/Article1-631573.aspx |archivedate=2011-02-08 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Bollywood/Bent-on-that-buick/Article1-702546.aspx |title=Bent on that buick |work=Hindustan Times |accessdate=2011-06-28 |date=2011-05-27 |author=Hiren Kotwani |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121022095425/http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Bollywood/Bent-on-that-buick/Article1-702546.aspx |archivedate=2012-10-22 }}</ref>。曾与卓娅在《幸运机会》共事的[[摄影师|摄影师]]卡洛斯·卡塔兰“想不加修饰”，尽可能地给予影片真实感，希望三个主演“晒黑”<ref name=zoyahindu/>。

卡特里娜的出场镜头在一处[[裸体海滩|裸体海滩]]拍摄。拍摄期间他们要求泳客走出取景范围，使得电影不会遭到印度审查机构的反对<ref name=rediffspainzoya>{{cite web|url=http://www.rediff.com/movies/slide-show/slide-show-1-zoya-akhtar-on-zindagi-na-milegi-dobara/20110707.htm?print=true|title=Zoya Akhtar on Zindagi Na Milegi Dobara|publisher=Rediff|accessdate=2011-07-13|date=2011-07-07|author=Patcy N|archive-date=2012-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121026081045/http://www.rediff.com/movies/slide-show/slide-show-1-zoya-akhtar-on-zindagi-na-milegi-dobara/20110707.htm?print=true|dead-url=no}}</ref>。布尼奥尔的[[番茄大战|番茄大战]]节为了配合歌曲《Ik Junoon》再次举办。约16吨价值1亿卢比（约合15万美元）的西红柿从葡萄牙运抵取景地<ref>{{cite news |url=http://newindianexpress.com/entertainment/hindi/article418606.ece |title=Nothing by chance |work=The New Indian Express |accessdate=2011-02-30 |date=2011-07-13 |author=Neelima Menon |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6AU98NZ3H?url=http://newindianexpress.com/entertainment/hindi/article418606.ece |archivedate=2012-09-06 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。起初赫里尼克和卡特琳娜两人不愿意拍摄亲吻的镜头，但最终还是拍了<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/celebrities/features/type/view/id/2356|title=Zoya's dilemma over Hrithik and Katrina's kiss in Zindagi Na Milegi Dobara|publisher=Bollywood Hungama|accessdate=2012-02-20|date=2011-06-23|author=Bollywood Hungama News Network|archive-date=2014-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140203051252/http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/celebrities/features/type/view/id/2356|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歌曲片段《{{le|小姐 (歌曲)|Señorita (Farhan Akhtar, Hrithik Roshan, Abhay Deol and Maria del Mar Fernández song)|小姐}}》在[[韦尔瓦省|韦尔瓦省]]小镇[[阿拉哈尔|阿拉哈尔]]拍摄。当地人警告剧组成员，称歌曲片段在晚上拍摄时音量太大。在当地拍摄的第三天，当地人身着盛装，阿拉哈尔市长加入他们拍摄影片<ref name=rediffspainzoya/> 。影片高潮的[[奔牛节|奔牛节]]场面在[[潘普洛纳|潘普洛纳]]拍摄<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/celebrities/features/type/view/id/1227|title=Check Out: Hrithik, Farhan, Abhay running with the bulls|publisher=Bollywood Hungama|accessdate=2011-12-30|date=2010-07-21|author=Bollywood Hungama News Network|archive-date=2014-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140203051257/http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/celebrities/features/type/view/id/1227|dead-url=no}}</ref>。影片于2010年12月在孟买的[[阿利巴格|阿利巴格]]和{{le|瓦阿什|Vashi}}杀青<ref name=znmdfinalschedule>{{cite news|title=Hrithik shoots for Zindagi Na Milegi Dobara|work=The Indian Express|accessdate=2011-11-28|url=http://www.indianexpress.com/news/Hrithik-shoots-for-Zindagi-Na-Milegi-Dobara/725202/|date=2010-12-17|author=Geety Sahgal}}</ref>。

== 原声带 ==
作曲三人组{{le|尚卡尔-伊哈桑-莱伊|Shankar-Ehsaan-Loy}}此前曾分别于《{{le|摇滚起来|Rock On!!}}》和《{{le|我来电|Karthik Calling Karthik}}》与阿克塔尔和卡特琳娜有过合作，此次为电影谱写配乐。三人组找来西班牙[[佛朗明哥歌唱|弗拉明戈歌手]]{{le|玛丽亚·德尔·玛尔·费尔南德斯|Maria del Mar Fernández}}演唱[[弗拉明戈|弗拉明戈]]歌曲《{{lang|es|Señorita}}》，这是她首次为电影献唱<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rediff.com/movies/review/music-review-zindagi-na-milegi-dobara/20110610.htm|title=Review: Zindagi Na Milegi... music is delightful|publisher=Rediff|accessdate=2011-07-09|date=2011-06-10|author=Sukanya Verma|archive-date=2011-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110704043912/http://www.rediff.com/movies/review/music-review-zindagi-na-milegi-dobara/20110610.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。阿布依·多尔与另两位主演李提克·罗森和法尔汗·阿赫塔尔一起唱歌，这是他首次唱歌<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.sify.com/movies/abhay-deol-sings-again-news-bollywood-lkgjwwdfbag.html?ref=false|title=Abhay Deol sings again!|publisher=Sify|accessdate=2011-12-30|date=2011-10-06|author=Indo-Asian News Service|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141011225828/http://www.sify.com/movies/abhay-deol-sings-again-news-bollywood-lkgjwwdfbag.html?ref=false|archive-date=2014-10-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。原声带发行后获得音评人的积极评价，在音乐榜单上获得显著关注。

