s/mumbai/music-launch-zindagi-na-milegi-dobara/articleshow/8822706.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歌曲《Khaabon Kay Parinday》和《Dil Dhadakne Do》的宣传片于接下来一个星期发行。法尔汗·阿赫塔尔和{{le|瑞塔许·西汪尼|Ritesh Sidhwani}}透过[[Facebook|Facebook印度]]宣传了这部电影<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/media/set/?set=a.195382107177243.51911.176228295759291|title=Niet compatibele browser|publisher=Facebook|accessdate=2011-07-04|archive-date=2016-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160201031737/https://www.facebook.com/media/set/?set=a.195382107177243.51911.176228295759291|dead-url=no}}</ref>。电影推介新闻发布会于7月1日在[[昌迪加尔|昌迪加尔]]举行<ref>{{cite news|url=http://daily.bhaskar.com/article/CHD-pics-katrina-farhan-and-abhay-charm-chandigarh-2234577.html?HF-4=|title=Katrina, Farhan, Abhay charm Chandigarh with 'Zindagi Milegi Na Dobara'|work=Dainik Bhaskar|accessdate=2011-07-04|date=2011-07-03|author=DNA India|archive-date=2011-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110707110045/http://daily.bhaskar.com/article/CHD-pics-katrina-farhan-and-abhay-charm-chandigarh-2234577.html?HF-4=|dead-url=no}}</ref>。电影两段对白宣传片7月3日发布。剧组成员于7月7日踏上从孟买到德里的巡演之旅，途径苏拉特、巴罗达、艾哈迈达巴德、乌代布尔、阿杰梅尔和斋浦尔，古尔冈音乐会将路演推向高潮<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Bollywood/Zindagi-Na-Milegi-Dobara-cast-ready-to-hit-the-road/Article1-717061.aspx |title=Zindagi Na Milegi Dobara cast ready to hit the road |work=Hindustan Times |accessdate=2011-07-04 |date=2011-07-04 |author=Prashant Singh |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121022095443/http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Bollywood/Zindagi-Na-Milegi-Dobara-cast-ready-to-hit-the-road/Article1-717061.aspx |archivedate=2012-10-22 }}</ref>。影片原定在全球公映前夕于{{le|第12届印度国际电影学会奖|12th IIFA Awards}}上首映，但最终取消<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sify.com/movies/zindagi-na-milegi-dobara-to-premiere-at-iifa-news-bollywood-ldlpSzajaej.html|title=Zindagi Na Milegi Dobara to premiere at IIFA?|publisher=Sify|accessdate=2012-02-20|date=2011-03-11|author=Bollywood Hungama|archive-date=2014-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140320201421/http://www.sify.com/movies/zindagi-na-milegi-dobara-to-premiere-at-iifa-news-bollywood-ldlpSzajaej.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

影片发行方与[[激浪|激浪]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1nMU5YBi-UEM|title=Mountain Dew Zindagi na Milegi Dobara TVC|publisher=YouTube|accessdate=2011-07-04|date=2011-07-01|author=Mountains Dew Pakistan|archive-date=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219144647/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1nMU5YBi-UE|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[吉列|吉列]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k8po0jUu9AM|title=ZNMD in association with Gillette – Zindigi Na Milegi Dobaara|publisher=YouTube|accessdate=2011-07-04|date=2011-06-23|author=Gillette India|archive-date=2014-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140625035339/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k8po0jUu9AM|dead-url=no}}</ref>和{{le|ING Vysya银行|ING Vysya Bank}}开展广泛的宣传<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=amUcKPIV7Ys|title=Zindagi Na Milegi Dobara (ZNMD) and ING Life Co – branded Promo|publisher=YouTube|accessdate=2011-07-04|date=2011-07-01|author=Countryroadish|archive-date=2014-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140625035303/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=amUcKPIV7Ys|dead-url=no}}</ref>。影片的官方游戏改编自番茄大战节，由Jump Games于2011年7月19日在全移动平台上发布<ref name=znmdgame>{{cite news|title=Indian gaming industry to touch Rs 14bn in 2011|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2011-08-16/hardware/29892166_1_gaming-industry-gaming-market-jump-games|work=The Times of India|accessdate=2012-02-20|date=2011-08-16|author=Indu Nandakumar|archive-date=2013-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130505054632/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2011-08-16/hardware/29892166_1_gaming-industry-gaming-market-jump-games|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

