RK-for-throwing-party-days-after-blasts/818707/|accessdate=2011-07-20|title=Sena slams SRK for throwing party days after blasts|work=The Indian Express|date=2011-07-17|author=IE Agencies}}</ref>。影片制片方向马哈拉施特拉邦政府捐赠了包含从约10家孟买影院筹集款项的支票，用作对爆炸遇难者的捐赠<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/news/1392293/Makers-of-ZNMD-hand-over-a-cheque-to-CM-for-Mumbai-blast-victims|title=Makers of ZNMD hand over a cheque to CM for Mumbai blast victims|publisher=Bollywood Hungama|accessdate=2012-02-20|date=2011-11-21|author=Bollywood Hungama News Network|archive-date=2016-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160201031737/http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/news/1392293/Makers-of-ZNMD-hand-over-a-cheque-to-CM-for-Mumbai-blast-victims|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年3月24日，影片在英国[[高威科姆|高威科姆]][[白金汉郡新大学|白金汉郡新大学]]专门放映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/bollywood/interviews/a372678/katrina-kaif-interview-i-have-a-strong-connection-with-the-uk.html|title=Katrina Kaif interview: 'I have a strong connection with the UK'|publisher=Digital Spy|author=Steven Baker|date=2012-03-22|accessdate=2012-04-01|archive-date=2012-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120325161854/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/bollywood/interviews/a372678/katrina-kaif-interview-i-have-a-strong-connection-with-the-uk.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

