 |archivedate=2011-07-19 
 }}</ref>。《{{le|印度周刊|India Weekly}}》的{{le|施福什·库马尔|Shivesh Kumar}}给予影片四星<ref name=iw>{{cite web |url=http://www.IndiaWeekly.com/MovieRatings |title=IndiaWeekly's Movie Ratings |publisher=IndiaWeekly |accessdate=2011-09-13 |author=Shivesh Kumar |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110830082836/http://www.indiaweekly.com/MovieRatings/ |archivedate=2011-08-30 }}</ref>。{{le|Bollywood Hungama|Bollywood Hungama}}的{{le|塔兰·阿达什|Taran Adarsh}}给予影片3.5星，称它是一种“更加进化、成熟且让有知识的电影院观众做好准备支持的电影新流派<ref name=bhungamareview>{{cite web |url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Bollywood/ZNMD-gets-mixed-reaction-from-critics/Article1-721461.aspx |title=ZNMD gets mixed reaction from critics |work=Hindustan Times |accessdate=2011-12-30 |date=2011-07-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110818041653/http://www.hindustantimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/ZNMD-gets-mixed-reaction-from-critics/Article1-721461.aspx |archivedate=2011-08-18 }}</ref>。”《[[印度时报|印度时报]]》的尼哈特·卡米兹给予影片3.5星，并称其主演的表现：“如果阿布依是小队的支柱，法尔汗的幽默大师角色精力充沛，李提克从拘谨、只顾赚钱的股票经纪人转变为无忧无虑的流浪汉都是一个阶层的行为<ref>{{cite web|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/movie-reviews/hindi/Zindagi-Na-Milegi-Dobara/movie-review/9224624.cms|title=Zindagi Na Milegi Dobara movie review|work=The Times of India|accessdate=2011-07-15|date=2011-07-14|author=Nikhat Kazmi|archive-date=2011-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111204023906/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/movie-reviews/hindi/Zindagi-Na-Milegi-Dobara/movie-review/9224624.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

[[新德里电视台|新德里电视台]]的S·查特吉（S Chatterjee）给予影片3星对影片的老旧理念持保留意见，称赞卓娅·阿克塔尔的导演，表示“卓娅·阿克塔尔用美丽轻盈的触觉和些许温柔风趣发觉了传说故事，带来了能承载剧情的新鲜感<ref name=ndtvreview>{{cite web|title=Review: Zindagi Na Milegi Dobara|url=http://movies.ndtv.com/movie_review.aspx?id=637&albumname=Zindagi%20Na%20Milegi%20Dobara|work=NDTV|accessdate=2011-07-15|date=2011-07-15|author=Saibal Chatterjee|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110816063758/http://movies.ndtv.com/movie_review.aspx?id=637&albumname=Zindagi%20Na%20Milegi%20Dobara|archivedate=2011-08-16}}</ref>。Rediff.com的谢赫·阿亚玆（Shaikh Ayaz）给予影片3.5星，认为卓娅·阿克塔尔虽然将熟悉的情节放到一起，但影片的清新活力具有娱乐性。他写道，”阿克塔尔的爽朗角色给这部本来非常平淡的影片泵入新鲜活力<ref name=rediffreview>{{cite web|title=Review: Zindagi Na Milegi Dobara is fresh|url=http://www.rediff.com/movies/review/review-zindagi-na-milegi-dobara-is-fresh/20110715.htm|publisher=[[Rediff|Rediff]]|accessdate=2011-07-15|date=2011-07-15|author=Shaikh Ayaz|archive-date=2011-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716232056/http://www.rediff.com/movies/review/review-zindagi-na-milegi-dobara-is-fresh/20110715.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。“[[今日印度|今日印度]]的卡弗雷·巴穆扎（Kaveree Bamzai）对阿克塔尔的导演也是赞不绝口，表示：“看完影片的时候我坚信没有一段爱情能像一位女性那样美丽”，给予影片4星<ref>{{cite web|url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/site/story/zindagi-milegi-na-dobara-movie-review/1/144897.html|title='Zindagi Milegi Na Dobara' review|work=India Today|accessdate=2011-07-15|date=2011-07-15|author=Kaveree Bamzai|archive-date=2011-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110715205300/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/site/story/zindagi-milegi-na-dobara-movie-review/1/144897.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

影评人苏巴斯·K·贾哈（Subhash K Jha）给予影片3.5星，表示“愿上帝保佑卓娅的审美观，她将我们引入到美丽的瞬间，没有给我们任何理由去坚信最弥足珍贵的真理被肮脏包裹着<ref name=subhashkjhareview>{{cite web|title=Zindagi Na Milegi Dobara Review|url=http://www.nowrunning.com/movie/7770/bollywood.hindi/zindagi-na-milegi-dobara/3207/review.htm|publisher=Nowrunning.com|accessdate=2011-12-30|date=2011-07-16|author=Subhash K. Jha|archive-date=2011-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110914150139/http://www.nowrunning.com/movie/7770/bollywood.hindi/zindagi-na-milegi-dobara/3207/review.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”《[[每日新闻分析报|每日新闻分析报]]》的布莱西·查蒂亚（Blessy Chettiar）指出影片的音乐和法尔汗·阿克塔尔的演技是影片的亮点：“针对这些，编剧使用重剂量的象征。布拉瓦海岸的深海潜水、塞维利亚的高空跳伞和潘普洛纳的圣佛明奔牛节，别忘了阿琼终于付出行动的布尼奥尔番茄大战。害怕被淹死，在蓝天中放开身姿，结束于暴怒公牛的仁慈”，给予影片3星<ref name=dnareview>{{cite web|title=Zindagi Na Milegi Dobara review|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/entertainment/report_zindagi-na-milegi-dobara-review_1565930|work=DNA India|accessdate=2011-07-15|date=2011-07-15|author=Blessy Chettiar|archive-date=2011-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110717132052/http://www.dnaindia.com/entertainment/report_zindagi-na-milegi-dobara-review_1565930|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《{{le|CNN-IBN|CNN-IBN}}》的{{le|拉杰夫·马桑德|Rajeev Masand}}表示：“影片制造了有趣的轻松基调，所有男孩的西班牙之旅带给你为什么我们应该过着争分夺秒并追随内心的人生的深刻并发自内心的消息。”他还赞扬演员的表现，强调这是影片的主要积极因素，但他指出影片的片场“破坏了旅行之外的乐趣”，并打出3.5星<ref name=masandverdict>{{cite web|title=Singin’ in (the) Spain!|url=http://www.rajeevmasand.com/reviews/our-films/singin-in-the-spain/comment-page-1/#comment-3942|publisher=Rajeev Masand|accessdate=2011-07-15|date=2011-07-15|author=Rajeev Masand|archive-date=2011-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110720125834/http://www.rajeevmasand.com/reviews/our-films/singin-in-the-spain/comment-page-1/#comment-3942|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。相反，Rediff的拉贾·森（Raja Sen）称影片“很难做到有趣”，给予其1.5星<ref name=rediffrajasen>{{cite web|title=Raja Sen reviews Zindagi Na Milegi Dobara|url=http://www.rediff.com/movies/review/review-zindagi-na-milegi-dobara-raja/20110715.htm|publisher=Rediff|accessdate=2011-07-15|date=2011-07-15|author=Raja Sen|archive-date=2011-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110718112304/http://www.rediff.com/movies/review/review-zindagi-na-milegi-dobara-raja/20110715.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《[[卫报|卫报]]》的瑞安·吉尔贝伊（{{lang|en|Ryan Gilbey}}）大致上称赞该片：“这部影片仍可以放给全家人看，你可以知道原因。电影可能有点华而不实，不过影片中代表着各大西班牙城市的旅游局员工并非唯一跑出来笑嘻嘻的人。”但他表示电影是一部“倔强地反大男子主义”的伙伴电影<ref name=guardianreview>{{cite web|title=Ryan Gilbey's Bollywood contract: Hindi heroes pack a soft and hard punch|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/filmblog/2011/aug/02/ryan-gilbey-bollywood-contract|work=The Guardian|accessdate=2011-08-02|date=2011-08-02|author=Ryan Gilbey|archive-date=2013-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130211031915/http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/filmblog/2011/aug/02/ryan-gilbey-bollywood-contract|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《{{le|全国报|The National (Abu Dhabi)}}》评论员卡勒姆·阿夫塔卜（Kaleem Aftab）在他的四星评价中指出：“将旅行、浪漫喜剧和哥俩好动作扔进单一的场面也许像是一道拙劣的马萨拉混搭，但像所有好菜那样，配料与亲情的混搭创造了本年度最好的自我感觉良好影片之一<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thenational.ae/arts-culture/film/zindagi-na-milegi-dobara|accessdate=2011-08-12|title=Zindagi Na Milegi Dobara|date=2011-08-11|author=Kaleem Aftab|archive-date=2011-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110816065751/http://www.thenational.ae/arts-culture/film/zindagi-na-milegi-dobara|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

