== 续集 ==
影片发行后，卓娅·阿克塔尔表达了制作影片续集的想法。谈到这一想法时，她表示：“你永远不知道我会不会做续集。一切取决于正确的内容<ref>{{cite news|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2011-07-21/news-interviews/29798948_1_hangover-sequel-znmd-hrithik|title=Hrithik high on ZNMD sequel|work=The Times of India|accessdate=2011-11-27|date=2011-07-21|author=Renuka Vyavahare|archive-date=2013-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004230648/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2011-07-21/news-interviews/29798948_1_hangover-sequel-znmd-hrithik|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”据报道，如果续集被正式推出，一众演员希望在影片中再度出演自己的角色<ref>{{cite news|url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/zoya-akhtar-zindagi-na-milegi-dobara-hrithik-roshan-katrina-kaif-dil-chahta-hai-harry-potter-and-the-deathly-hallows-part-2-farhan-akhtar/1/145267.html|title=Zoya Akhtar is planning a sequel of ZNMD|work=India Today|accessdate=2012-03-02|date=2011-07-18|author=Priyanka Shrivastava|archive-date=2012-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120424043027/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/zoya-akhtar-zindagi-na-milegi-dobara-hrithik-roshan-katrina-kaif-dil-chahta-hai-harry-potter-and-the-deathly-hallows-part-2-farhan-akhtar/1/145267.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在接受《[[印度斯坦时报|印度斯坦时报]]》采访时，赫里尼克表达了续集基本剧情的构思。他表示续集可能设置在本作五年后，原班人马将变老，有理由继续另一段旅程。也与人同意需要一个合适的剧本，因为这不属于电影“商业领域”范畴<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Bollywood/Zindagi-Na-Milegi-Dobara-sequel-on-the-cards/Article1-733502.aspx |title=Zindagi Na Milegi Dobara sequel on the cards? |work=Hindustan Times |accessdate=2012-03-02 |date=2011-08-15 |author=Roshmila Bhattacharya |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407095027/http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Bollywood/Zindagi-Na-Milegi-Dobara-sequel-on-the-cards/Article1-733502.aspx |archivedate=2014-04-07 }}</ref>。然而，尽管有很多观众请求，但续集还是没有正式确认<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.indianexpress.com/news/ZNMD-sequel-not-on-the-cards--Zoya-Akhtar/829774/|title=ZNMD sequel not on the cards: Zoya Akhtar|work=The Indian Express|author=IE Agencies|accessdate=2012-03-02|date=2011-08-10}}</ref>。在印度国际电影学会奖典礼结束后，法尔汗·阿克塔尔评论道，“没有必要”拍续集<ref>{{cite news|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-06-13/news-interviews/32174165_1_technical-awards-farhan-akhtar-iifa-weekend|title='Zindagi Na Milegi Dobara' sequel not necessary: Farhan Akhtar|work=The Times of India|date=2012-06-13|author=Indo-Asian News Service|accessdate=2012-07-03}}{{Dead link}}</ref>。后来在2013年，卓娅接受《印度斯坦时报》采访时表达了完成她的第二部于2015年6月上映的电影《{{le|心跳零距离|Dil Dhadakne Do}}》的拍摄后，投入到剧本创作的兴趣<ref>{{cite web|last1=Adivarekar|first1=Priya|title=Zoya’s next titled Dil Dhadakne Do|url=http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/screen/zoyas-next-titled-dil-dhadakne-do/|website=India Express|accessdate=2014-07-24|archive-date=2014-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140803101743/http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/screen/zoyas-next-titled-dil-dhadakne-do/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

